### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/users HTTP/1.1

### Add a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "1",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### Update a user
PUT http://localhost:3000/users/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Phawat"
}

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/1 HTTP/1.1